sub_title: Math Manager at GLI Europe B.V.
summary: I am Math Manager at GLI Europe B.V. in Haarlem (NL). I run a team of 25+ Math Analysts expert in certifications for the Gaming Industry. I am expert in the analysis of Random Number Generators (RNGs) and their jurisdictional requirements for the Gaming industry across the world. I am focusing more and more on Data Science in the Python framework (pandas, numpy, scikit-learn).
